org.javafp.data

Class IList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.javafp.data.IList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - element type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IList.Empty, IList.NonEmpty

    public abstract class IList<T>
extends Object
implements Iterable<T>
    Simple recursive, immutable linked list. This list type allows tails to be shared between lists. It does not allow null values to be held in the list.
